19:29.280 --> 19:30.910
I've been hounded by the police,

19:30.960 --> 19:33.590
I've had wild accusations
thrown at me by the press.

19:33.640 --> 19:38.630
I've been defamed and vilified
by politicians of every stripe.

19:38.680 --> 19:42.830
