20:19.720 --> 20:21.550
You wanted me to throw the
cards out, do you remember?

20:21.600 --> 20:24.390
Yes, that's what I'm talking about.

20:24.440 --> 20:26.990
I wanted to throw them out,
you said, "No, fuck you,"

20:27.040 --> 20:30.550
