you going? Can I come?

21:43.120 --> 21:46.390
(Birthday! Birthday!)

21:46.440 --> 21:48.710
- Alright, you can come...
- Good.

21:48.760 --> 21:49.870
.. little boy.

21:49.920 --> 21:51.030
There you go.

21:51.080 --> 21:53.870
But he is moving back in.

21:53.920 --> 21:56.880
With us? Cool!

21:58.760 --> 22:02.470
So I said to him -- I mean,
this is on air, mind you --

22:02.520 --> 22:04.550
