22:52.800 --> 22:54.310
Yeah, Jizz Monkey.

22:54.360 --> 22:56.910
I need you to make me a call.

22:56.960 --> 22:59.990
No, I'm gonna need a
little bit more this time.

23:03.240 --> 23:05.990
You are Cal McGregor!

23:17.230 --> 23:18.230
Hey.

23:18.280 --> 23:19.950
Hey. Where are you?

23:20.000 --> 23:22.390
I'm just about to go into a meeting.

23:22.440 --> 23:23.790
Gav's talking about another book.

23:23.840 --> 23:26.030
Another book? What would
that one be about?

23:26.080 --> 23:29.790
My treatise on democracy
and why it doesn't work.

23:29.840 --> 23:32.550
And why you should be
our benevolent dictator?

23:32.600 --> 23:35.340
Oh, there's a bestseller right there.

23:36.200 --> 23:38.390
Hey, we need to talk, you know.

23:38.440 --> 23:39.470
Yeah.

23:39.520 --> 23:41.310
Why didn't anyone tell me?

23:41.360 --> 23:42.790
