24:14.000 --> 24:15.630
Nuh.

24:15.680 --> 24:18.020
- Did you tell David?
- No.

24:19.440 --> 24:23.070
Oh, we just keep fighting.
And it's no-one's fault.

24:23.120 --> 24:26.150
