I have no intention of blowing off Nicole.

24:50.480 --> 24:53.110
Sorry, poor choice of words. I...

24:58.000 --> 25:01.750
Barney, if we are going to
act on this, then that's it.

25:01.800 --> 25:03.560
To the end.

25:05.160 --> 25:06.870
We can never know that.

25:06.920 --> 25:08.400
I know.

25:12.800 --> 25:14.680
Patience.

25:17.280 --> 25:18.590
I've gotta go.

25:18.640 --> 25:20.150
OK.

25:20.200 --> 25:22.550
I've got that big bash tonight, whoo-hoo!

25:22.600 --> 25:23.950
OK!

25:24.000 --> 25:25.310
I'll call you later.

25:25.360 --> 25:27.470
Hey, don't have too much fun.

25:27.520 --> 25:29.720
Don't worry, I won't.

25:31.160 --> 25:32.630
♪ You're the one

