key, then you can go home.

28:11.920 --> 28:13.670
Have a good night, Cleave.
See you in the morning.

28:13.720 --> 28:19.320
Oh, yeah, enjoy your fancy
Northern Beaches wankers' parties.

28:21.840 --> 28:23.110
Wendy!

28:23.160 --> 28:24.230
