all the time in the world,

31:30.080 --> 31:31.390
haven't we, darling?

31:31.440 --> 31:34.030
- Ruth...
- What did I do?

31:34.080 --> 31:36.070
What did I fucking do?

31:36.120 --> 31:39.110
Because I used to be a
good cop before I met you.

31:39.160 --> 31:42.120
I made my parents proud before I met you.

31:43.240 --> 31:48.030
But I have betrayed everything
I believed in... for you.

31:48.080 --> 31:53.550
And you... you were just using me.

31:53.600 --> 31:57.560
Darling, we just need
to make a fresh start.

32:07.600 --> 32:09.540
A fresh start it is.

32:27.840 --> 32:29.880
Hi, it's me.

32:31.000 --> 32:34.080
I know I said you could
have the night off but, um...

32:36.360 --> 32:39.640
.. er, we have a little situation.

32:41.280 --> 32:43.350
Not Buon Riccordo, then?

32:43.400 --> 32:45.630
