you borrowed my car.

33:03.800 --> 33:06.800
- Where the fuck are we?
- Oh, here we go.

33:06.960 --> 33:09.560
What the fuck is this? We only...

33:11.000 --> 33:15.830
Oh, not the bowlo. Not a surprise party!

33:15.880 --> 33:17.360
Oh, Wendy!

33:18.440 --> 33:20.910
Oh, not a surprise party!

33:20.960 --> 33:22.270
Don't spoil it!

33:22.320 --> 33:25.510
How can you spoil something that's rancid?

33:25.560 --> 33:27.230
- Oh, thank you very much.
